Description:
Leap forward and strike the ground with arcane force dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Slam.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_arcane_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage to all targets within &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_Flail.Spell_Flail_Slam_AOE.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; of the impact. 


Leave behind a hazardous area at the impact point that inflicts a stack of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Impairment&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt; to all targets that enter.


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Impairment&lt;/font&gt; deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;&lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_arcane_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage per second and inflicts &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;weaken&lt;/font&gt;, reducing their base damage by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.DMGStandard * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.StackMax]} stacks)&lt;/font&gt;


This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

Allies that enter the hazardous area obtain &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Deflecting Frailty&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Slam_AllyBuff_WeakenAttackers.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;, which when attacked will inflict a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;stacking weaken&lt;/font&gt; to enemy attackers when hit, reducing the enemy's damage dealt by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Slam_WeakenStack.DMGStandard * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; per stack for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Slam_WeakenStack.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Slam_WeakenStack.StackMax]} stacks)&lt;/font&gt;


Additionally while the effect is active, when allies are hit, they gain &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[GlobalAbilityTable.Global_Flail_SlamAbility_Lifesteal.DmgPctToHealth * 100]}% lifesteal for &lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Slam_Lifesteal_Tracker.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. 

(Deflecting Frailty scales with Focus, increasing its duration to up to &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Slam_AllyBuff_WeakenAttackers.DurationAttbScalingMaxValue]}&lt;/font&gt; seconds.)

Swirl the flail above the player's head dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;4&lt;/font&gt; rapid hits of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Blast.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_arcane_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage in a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;3m&lt;/font&gt; radius around the player. 


After the first spin is completed, trigger a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_Flail.Spell_Flail_AuraBlast_AOE.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; blast of energy granting &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_AuraBlast_Empower.DMGStandard * 100]}% empower&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_AuraBlast_Empower.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt; to all allies inside the radius.


This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

All allies within &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_Flail.Spell_Flail_AuraBlast_AOE_Upgraded.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; of player during the arcane vortex are &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;cleansed&lt;/font&gt; of crowd control status effects (Root, Stun, Slow) and are immune to them for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_AuraBlast_CCEffectImmunity.BaseDuration]}&lt;/font&gt; seconds. 


All allies inside are also &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;healed&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_AuraBlast_Heal.HealthModifierDamageBased * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; weapon damage. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Healing scales exclusively with Focus)&lt;/font&gt; 

(Crowd Control Immunity scales with Focus, increasing its duration to up to &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_AuraBlast_CCEffectImmunity.DurationAttbScalingMaxValue]}&lt;/font&gt; seconds.)

Drag the head of the flail against the ground causing an eruption of arcane energy in front of the player, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Burst.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_arcane_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and inflicting &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;two stacks&lt;/font&gt; of &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Impairment&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt; to all targets hit.


Automatically follow up with an additional melee attack that deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Burst_FollowUp.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage.


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Impairment&lt;/font&gt; deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_arcane_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage per second and inflicts &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;weaken&lt;/font&gt;, reducing their base damage by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.DMGStandard * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Max {[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_HexDoT.StackMax]} stacks)&lt;/font&gt;

Abilities and Heavy attack hits against targets with less than &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive1.TargetHealthPercent]}%&lt;/font&gt; health, increase incoming healing by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Passive_OnHitLowHP_Anointed.HealMod * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; and gain &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Passive_OnHitLowHP_Haste.MoveSpeedMod * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt; haste&lt;/font&gt; to self for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Passive_OnHitLowHP_Anointed.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. 
(Incoming healing increase scales with Focus, increasing its power to up to &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Passive_OnHitLowHP_Anointed.PotencyAttbScalingMaxValue * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;) 


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Haste increases movement speed)&lt;/font&gt;

Grants &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Cooldown Reduction&lt;/font&gt; based on actions performed in different &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;equip loads&lt;/font&gt;:
	\n\n•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Heavy&lt;/font&gt; - &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive2.CooldownTimer * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; cooldown reduction when hit or blocking a hit. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;({[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive2.ActivationCooldown]}s cooldown)&lt;/font&gt; 
	\n•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Medium&lt;/font&gt; - 
	&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive2_Helper_Med.CooldownTimer * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; cooldown reduction when dodging an attack. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;({[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive2_Helper_Med.ActivationCooldown]}s cooldown)&lt;/font&gt; 
	\n•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Light&lt;/font&gt; - &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive2_Helper_Light.CooldownTimer * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; cooldown reduction when hitting a target. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;({[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Eldritch_Passive2_Helper_Light.ActivationCooldown]}s cooldown)&lt;/font&gt;

Sprint forward up to &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;10m&lt;/font&gt;. Upon reactivating the ability, pressing basic attack, or reaching the end of the sprint, leap forward up to an additional &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;6m&lt;/font&gt; and slam to the ground, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Charge_FlippingAttack.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage to targets in range of the flail during the leap and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Charge.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage upon landing, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggering&lt;/font&gt; targets on impact.


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Character collision is disabled while sprinting forward)&lt;/font&gt;


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your Flail, this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_Charge.TauntDuration]}s when it hits. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

Grants a bonus to Barrage based on what &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;shield type&lt;/font&gt; is equipped:


•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Round Shield&lt;/font&gt; - Barrage hits for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Upgrade_Flail_Charge_Upgrade2.BaseDamage * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; more base weapon damage.

•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Kite Shield&lt;/font&gt; - Barrage hits inflict &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Charge_Slow.MoveSpeedMod * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt; slow&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;
	{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Charge_Slow.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(This will also slow targets moved through with the Bulldoze upgrade)&lt;/font&gt;

•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Tower Shield&lt;/font&gt; - Barrage gains &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt; while active.


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Slow reduces movement speed)&lt;/font&gt; 

&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

Hitting weakened targets with trip will inflict &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Trip_Rend.PhysicalArmor * -100]}% rend&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Trip_Rend.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt; on the target, and granting &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Trip_Fortify.PhysicalArmor * 100]}% &lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;fortify&lt;/font&gt; on self for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_Trip_Fortify.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;.


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Rend decreases armor)&lt;/font&gt; 

&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Fortify increases armor)&lt;/font&gt;

Perform a spinning leap then swing the flail down to strike targets, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_DefensiveStrike.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage.


While leaping, trigger a burst of energy, granting a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;reinforced fortify&lt;/font&gt; to self and all allies within &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;3m&lt;/font&gt; of player, increasing armor by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_DefensiveStrike_Reinforced.PhysicalArmor * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_DefensiveStrike_Reinforced.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt; or until &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_Flail_DefensiveStrike_Reinforced.StopOnHitCount]} hits&lt;/font&gt; are taken. 


This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;


&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your Flail, this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.1H_Flail_Ability_DefensiveStrike_TAUNT.TauntDuration]}s to all enemies within 8m. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

Grants status effect duration modifications on self based on what &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;shield type&lt;/font&gt; is equipped:


•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Round Shield&lt;/font&gt; - Increased base duration of all limited duration buffs on player by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Crusader_Passive3.StatusEffectDurationReduction * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;

•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Kite Shield&lt;/font&gt; - Decrease base duration of damage over time and debilitating effects on player by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Crusader_Passive3_Helper1.StatusEffectDurationReduction * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; 

•&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;Tower Shield&lt;/font&gt; - Decrease base duration of crowd control effects on player by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[FlailAbilityTable.Passive_Flail_Crusader_Passive3_Helper2.StatusEffectDurationReduction * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt;
